This will allow both current and prospective apprentices to be able to connect.

//Adding Friends

People will be able to filter by Company, University, Industry, Location, Interests, Age.
They will also be able to do a basic search by name.

//Chats

People will  be able to have both 1 on 1 chats and group chats with a number of people in it.
In this you will not only be able to message but you will be able to call, send polls and organise events.

//Connection Count

The connection count will be a number displayed that counts the total number of people that you have talked to.
There will be a badge system in place that takes the number of connections you have and rewards you with a virtual badge whenever you hit a connection goal. (10,50,100, etc)